// ================================
// SECTION: PRINCIPIOS DE MARCA
// ================================
section(class="py-24 bg-surface-dark/30 border-y border-white/5 relative" id="brand-principles")
  div(class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-primary/5 blur-[100px] pointer-events-none")

  div(class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6")
    div(class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-px bg-white/5 border border-white/5")

      // ----------------------------
      // BLOQUE 01: MISIÓN
      // ----------------------------
      div(class="bg-background-dark p-12 relative group overflow-hidden" id="mission")
        div(class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-30 transition-opacity")
          span(class="material-symbols-outlined text-6xl text-primary")
            | dynamic_form

        div(class="relative z-10")
          span(class="text-xs font-bold text-primary mb-4 block tracking-widest")
            | 01. MISIÓN
          h3(class="font-display font-bold text-2xl mb-6 uppercase")
            | Empoderar al Ecosistema
          p(class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-8")
            | Proveer infraestructura digital robusta que permita a los DJs y productores latinos gestionar su carrera con autonomía técnica y financiera.
          div(class="w-full h-1 bg-white/10 relative overflow-hidden")
            div(class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary w-1/3")

      // ----------------------------
      // BLOQUE 02: VISIÓN
      // ----------------------------
      div(class="bg-background-dark p-12 relative group overflow-hidden" id="vision")
        div(class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-30 transition-opacity")
          span(class="material-symbols-outlined text-6xl text-ritma-purple")
            | rocket_launch

        div(class="relative z-10")
          span(class="text-xs font-bold text-ritma-purple mb-4 block tracking-widest")
            | 02. VISIÓN
          h3(class="font-display font-bold text-2xl mb-6 uppercase")
            | Estándar Regional
          p(class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-8")
            | Ser el núcleo tecnológico donde converge la creatividad musical y la innovación, elevando la calidad de la producción latina al estándar global.
          div(class="w-full h-1 bg-white/10 relative overflow-hidden")
            div(class="absolute inset-0 bg-ritma-purple w-2/3")

      // ----------------------------
      // BLOQUE 03: VALORES
      // ----------------------------
      div(class="bg-background-dark p-12 relative group overflow-hidden" id="values")
        div(class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-30 transition-opacity")
          span(class="material-symbols-outlined text-6xl text-ritma-cyan")
            | diversity_3

        div(class="relative z-10")
          span(class="text-xs font-bold text-ritma-cyan mb-4 block tracking-widest")
            | 03. VALORES
          h3(class="font-display font-bold text-2xl mb-6 uppercase")
            | Comunidad & Ritmo
          p(class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-8")
            | Nuestra base es la transparencia, la innovación constante y el respeto profundo por la diversidad cultural de nuestras raíces.
          div(class="w-full h-1 bg-white/10 relative overflow-hidden")
            div(class="absolute inset-0 bg-ritma-cyan w-full")
